name: Unlock organizational network insights using Microsoft 365 datasets
description: Use this template to harness information flows and team connectivity to unlock productivity, explore influential connections, and empower inclusive networks. This template extracts Microsoft 365 data (Teams Chats, and Outlook Meetings and Emails) via Microsoft Graph Data Connect and aggregates with Azure Active Directory Users to produce analytics-ready data for analysis. Disclaimer: this template is in PREVIEW stage at this time. We would love to hear your thoughts on this template. Please send us your ideas and feedback at https://aka.ms/ona-m365-feedback.
author: Microsoft
